Package: shareIBC
Title: Share IBC
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Anderson", "Arroyo", , "a.arroyo@pucp.pe", role = c("cre", "aut"))
Description: Application of the Social Ministry at IBC Madrid created to
    allow members of the community to share job opportunities, offer their
    professional services, recycle and give away free items, request
    assistance and donate to the ministry.
